item.title: U.S.-India trade talks could get a boost as America sees life going on without it
item.description: There could be a renewed push to conclude a U.S.-India trade deal, analysts say, as the White House sees other countries signing trade deals.

item.title: The government is barreling toward a partial shutdown over DHS funding. Here's what to expect
